      passage: `The fact that publications by University of Minnesota economist Ellen R. McGrattan, who studies financial policy, are so frequently cited in other scholars&rsquo; work _____ the usefulness of her research for her peers&mdash;other economists clearly find her studies valuable for their own scholarship.`,
      prompt: `Which choice completes the text with the most logical and precise word or phrase?`,
